zoomer: view and click pictures

compiling (needs QT 4.4 or more):
	
	qmake
	make
	
running:
	
	./zoomer

zoomer reads the configuration file "zoomer.cfg", and writes the changes to it.
The configuration file is like this:

###########################
Click on front wheel			#message
620.999										#selection x
369.833										#selection y
6.00001										#zoom factor
100												#contrast (%)
0													#brightness
100												#gamma (%)
2													#number of the image (first = 1)
img/image_4_00035_07.tif	#list of image names
img/image_4_00035_08.tif	#
img/image_4_00035_09.tif	#
img/image_4_00035_10.tif	#
###########################



Thanks to http://qt4.digitalfanatics.org

